From what I have seen of Jersey it looks nice. Would be cool if it
required less annotations and supported more conventions. GetOrder
for example would map to Get, PostOrder to post etc. It did remind me
a bit of WCF with the URI mapping stuff, though more flexible. Still
much more limited than routes in rails or MVC routes.

Glenn



